# EVE Online Single Sign-On (SSO) Configuration
# 
# 1. Go to https://developers.eveonline.com/ and log in.
# 2. Create a new Application (Authentication & API Access).
# 3. Add scopes:
#    - esi-planets.manage_planets.v1
#    - esi-skills.read_skills.v1
# 4. Set the Callback URL to: http://localhost:5173/callback
# 5. Copy the Client ID from the application details page.
# 
# Copy this file to `.env` and replace the placeholder with your actual Client ID.

VITE_EVE_CLIENT_ID=your_client_id_here
